timeline.bodyText:
I would not hardcode that we always look in System properties then env then default. I would allow the following workflow:

Start from default;
Apply changes from env;
Apply changes from System properties;

BatchSpanProcessor.getBuilder().overwriteFromEnv().overwriteFromSystemProperties().build()

The default should be the proposed solution but would like if the users can also change this order if needed.
Thoughts on this?

